-- Villa Park to Host English Soccer’s Community Shield in August
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-18T13:58:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-18/villa-park-to-host-english-soccer-s-community-shield-in-august.html
Villa Park  will host next season’s
Community Shield game between Manchester City and Chelsea, the
Football Association said.  The traditional start to the English soccer season is
usually played at Wembley Stadium in London. With Wembley
hosting the final of the Olympic tournament on Aug. 11, the F.A.
moved the Community Shield to Aston Villa’s stadium.  Manchester United defeated Manchester City 3-2 in this
season’s Community Shield.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  